I have three desktops and one laptop all running XP Home and Pro.
I have a Maxtor DiamondMax 80 Gig drive in an external USB-2 case.
I move it all the time between all four PCs.
I have a folder for each PC set up on the drive and just drag and drop things I can't afford to loose like pictures and stuff to their respective folder.
Too easy.
I've never found any backup program without glitches or that wasn't a PITA to use.
Every few months I take those folders and burn them to DVD.
